entries.femaleVariant: V... You have to tell me what is happening.
The blood... You were out for hours. What's wrong?
Eh, it's nothing.
It's getting worse, Panam.
It's... nothing. I'm fine now.
Fuck, so I can see.
Will you tell me what is going on? Or will we keep playing this stupid charade?
Panam, I... It's getting worse, every single day...
OK, V, relax. Take it bit by bit. What is happening, exactly?
You know Johnny Silverhand?
It's the busted tech in my head.
I'm afraid to tell you the truth.
To tell you the whole truth... I'm afraid things won't be the same between us if I do.
V, listen to me.
V, cut the crap and tell me what's going on! I'm worried!
There is not a thing you could say to me that would change how...
I mean, just cut the bullshit and tell me what's going on!
You know Johnny Silverhand?
OK. So... You ever hear of the Relic?
The Arasaka tech? Does something with personalities? I saw the ads. Sounds like some rich people scam, to be honest.
It's not bullshit. I've got a biochip in my head with one of those constructs. And the chip's damaged.
So take it out!
Yes, they sometimes play those oldies on the radio. Why?
That's just it. Johnny's alive. He's sitting in my head.
He's what? A-am I not... is this some sort of strange metaphor?
V... Back to what we were saying...
Honestly? I dunno.
I'm afraid you can't.
Honestly? Not a clue.
But there has to be something, someone who can...
Remember Hellman? He's the one who created the personality construct tech.
That's why you wanted to get him.
Couldn't help me. Not sure anyone can.
I don't believe that.
But it was a dead end. Now I have to figure out where to go next.
You'll find a way. And once you do, let me know. I will help.
Thanks, Panam.
[Kiss Panam] Thanks for being here for me.
I'll be fine. You take care of yourself!
Thanks, Panam.
Thanks for everything.
I'll be fine, don't worry. Good luck with the new camp.
For being here for me.
Take care of yourself. And let me know... Well, just please keep in touch.
Want me to walk with you?
Thanks...
Take care, Panam!
I'm serious. It's a long story.
Silverhand's wreaking havoc in my head.
Long story. Got a job, fucked it up, now Silverhand's personality construct's sitting in my head.
Panam, Silverhand's construct is busy wreaking havoc in my head.
Bullshit.
Yeah, well, he's not too happy about it either. Turns out we don't really mix. And it's getting worse.
You are not joking.
Just trying to live with it. Survive, actually.
It's certainly not doing wonders for your health.
Impossible. It's not â€“ i-it's simply impossible. Johnny Silverhand?
Listen, did you try, you know... talking to someone about this?
Could tell my therapist a lotta things, but this isn't one of 'em. Construct's more like a cancer, growing every day.
More complicated than that. Relic's also keeping me alive.
The personality construct attacked my brain.
Definitely not that simple. Relic's also keeping me alive. But...
Chip held a personality construct. Construct attacked my brain.
So this is cyberpsychosis? Because if it is, I know people who--
No, no. The chip's data is infecting my neural connections. Got nothing to do with cyberpsychosis.
I remove the Relic, I die. If I don't deal with the construct, I die.
Fuck.
You can't reverse it somehow? Stop it? Fuck, you can't get it out of your head?
That's what I'm trying to do. But the clock's ticking. Getting worse by the day.
Fuck.
Where are we?
What happened?
Where... where are we?
What happened? I remember, I... We were talking, then suddenly...
I gotta go. I'm feeling better, really.
V! Welcome back to the land of the living!
I know this area, back from the old routes.
I thought I heard that voice!
I can stay for a bit. Thanks.
Remember â€“ our offer still stands.
See you made yourselves at home already.
Much better now. Thanks for your help.
Thanks, I'll stick around for a bit.
All fine now, thanks.
See you already settled in here.
We do have some experience in this.
This is a good place. We have greater control over the area. The rest will settle in quickly.
You passed out. Completely. We took you with us.
We moved camp. You are safe, everything is under control.
You passed out. Completely. We took you with us.
Somewhere new. We moved camp. Don't worry, we are safe here. For now.
I don't know...
Wait, I will go with you.
You really safe here, though?
About time sleeping beauty decided to join us! Hey there.
Hey, Mitch.
Took good care of your ride. She's over there.
Make yourself at home.
I'm glad to hear it.
If you need help, the Aldecaldos are here for you.
If you need anything, you know where to find us.
V?
Panam... I...
V, relax, everything is OK. How do you feel?
Where...?
Where?
Finally. We were worried.
Is everything OK?
But tell us, how are you? You scared us.
Thanks, but I gotta get going.
Thanks, Mitch. But I'd better be going.
You're barely standing, V. You take care of yourself, OK?
And that, at least, we can agree on.
I will not even pretend to understand. I don't think it has even sunk in yet. But I am serious â€“ how can I help?
This whole family will help. Saul was not joking. You understand?
For now, yes. Militech does not venture this far. And our vantage points really are much better.
But you know, everything here... It is temporary, all of it. We will soon have to decide what comes next.
But you're not leaving us already, are you?
Gotta go.
V? Talk to me?
Is anything wrong, V?
